ron","expr":"0 2 * * *","tz":"Asia/Shanghai"},"sessionTarget":"isolated","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"请执行每日自我反思任务：\n\n1. 查看过去24小时内的会话记录（使用 sessions_list --activeMinutes 1440）\n2. 分析每个会话：\n   - 什么做得好？（任务顺利完成、高效工具使用等）\n   - 什么出了问题？（错误、重试、误解等）\n   - 学到了什么？（具体、可操作的教训）\n3. 将反思结果写入适当的文件：\n   - 流程改进 → AGENTS.md\n   - 工具使用技巧 → TOOLS.md  \n   - 今日事件 → memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md\n   - 用户偏好 → memory/about-user.md\n4. 生成简短总结（2-4句话）\n\n5. 反思完成后，执行 GitHub 备份：\n   - 进入 workspace 目录\n   - git add .\n   - git commit -m \"每日反思更新: $(date +%Y-%m-%d)\"\n   - git push origin main\n\n注意：\n- 只提取真正的教训，不要简单总结\n- 检查是否已有类似记录，避免重复\n- 保持简洁具体，不要泛泛而谈\n- 确保备份包含所有更新后的文件"},"delivery":{"mode":"announce","channel":"feishu"},"state":{"nextRunAtMs":1774116000000,"lastRunAtMs":1774029600020,"lastRunStatus":"ok","lastStatus":"ok","lastDurationMs":51419,"lastDelivered":true,"lastDeliveryStatus":"delivered","consecutiveErrors":0}},{"id":"194a22c4-6729-48df-9b46-9781bda49270","agentId":"main","sessionKey":"agent:main:main","name":"起床提醒","enabled":true,"createdAtMs":1773934456464,"updatedAtMs":1774046711982,"schedule":{"expr":"45 6 * * *","kind":"cron","tz":"Asia/Shanghai"},"sessionTarget":"isolated","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"请发送一条温馨的起床提醒到飞书：☀️ 早上好！6:45啦！新的一天开始了，该起床啦！记得今天也要元气满满哦！💪"},"delivery":{"channel":"feishu","mode":"announce"},"state":{"nextRunAtMs":1774133100000,"lastRunAtMs":1774046700011,"lastRunStatus":"error","lastStatus":"error","lastDurationMs":11971,"lastDeliveryStatus":"delivered","consecutiveErrors":2,"lastError":"⚠️ ✉️ Message failed","lastDelivered":true}},{"id":"0358012e-72cc-4647-807b-7e6df61c1d4b","agentId":"main","sessionKey":"agent:main:main","name":"思考共产主义","enabled":false,"createdAtMs":1773933428718,"updatedAtMs":1774042225818,"schedule":{"expr":"0 * * * *","kind":"cron","tz":"Asia/Shanghai","staggerMs":300000},"sessionTarget":"isolated","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"请思考一下共产主义如何实现，从理论、实践、经济、社会等多个角度进行分析，并总